<h1>Amakozi Technologies expand to USA</h1>
<h3>Saturday, 01 Aug 2009</h3>
<p>Amakozi Technologies is proud to announce the opening of its USA subsidiary, Amakozi Technologies LLC</p>
<p>Based in California, the subsidiary was created in order to streamline the processes of doing business in the USA, and to provide local support to Amakozi Technologies' growing USA customer base.</p> <p>The subsidiary, owned by parent company Amakozi Technologies cc, will be managed by Nico Esterhuyse.  
Nico Esterhuyse, one of the senior technical consultants currently employed by Amakozi Technologies cc, will relocate to the USA to provide hands-on support for the newly created USA subsidiary as of January 2010.</p>                
<p>The administration of the entire group consisting of Amakozi Technologies cc (South African head office), Amakozi Technologies BV (Dutch subsidiary) and the newly formed Amakozi Technologies LLC is maintained by the head office in Somerset West, South Africa.</p>

